verse = \lyricmode {
  His wife be wi -- dowed and neg -- lect -- ed;
his chil -- dren or -- phaned, un -- pro -- tect -- ed.
And when they beg, let nought be giv -- en;
they from their ru -- ined homes be dri -- ven.
May cred -- i -- tors his goods all seize;
may stran -- gers plun -- der what they please.
}
